name: Ghosts Embrace #2
description:
Ghosts are living with us from birth to death.
Just need to look From a different angle.
There are lot of ghosts in our life that we're used to and feel them.
Maybe they're our friends or we are fighting with them!
Perhaps the attributes of human beings are the same as ghosts! 
Friendship, anger, kindness, helping, etc. Maybe they are all ghosts and We decide to make a connection with which one.
Maybe we'll be the ghost of other people's lives.
So Try to be a good person to be a good ghost of others' lives.
